            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社14日專訊》越疆(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02432:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02432\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02432-HK</a>)現價跌2.1%,報60.95元,該股成交約829萬股,涉資5.57億元,最高見71.4元,最多升14.7%,最低見58元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　越疆早前發布全球首款「靈巧雙臂+直膝行走」人形機器人,股價持續上升。股價周一(10日)收市36.45元,至今日最高價71.4元,期內股價最多升95.9%。</p></section><section><p class=\"\">　</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　現時,恒生指數報23556,升93點或升0.4%,主板成交超過360億元。國企指數報8702,升62點或升0.7%。恒生科技指數報5735,跌11點或跌0.2%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">(vs)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
